tika.dc.description: It's started to snow in Stoneybrook - school could be closed soon. Karen has lots of fun in the snow and she's also helping her brothers find snow-clearing jobs. But Karen's lined up too many customers, so when snow day finally comes there's no fun - only hard work shovelling snow!
